rency"}, {'post_id': 9, 'day': 8, 'content': 'Appreciate the transparency—latency and throughput data will be critical for our ROI calculations. Looking forward to comparing specs against our current vendor to validate the cost-per-inference case.', 'reply_to_agent_post_id': 2, 'source_group_id': 'E1', 'group_id': 'S1', 'customer_type': 'small', 'custom_name': None, 'persona_name': None, 'replying_to_your_post': "We hear you! Concrete benchmarks, API specs, and specialized use cases are coming. We're focused on quality and performance first. Stay tuned for our latency and throughput reports next week. #NovaMind #AI #Transparency"}, {'post_id': 8, 'day': 8, 'content': "This is exactly the transparency our enterprise teams need for serious integration decisions. Looking forward to those benchmarks—let's discuss a deeper partnership once you publish. 🤝", 'reply_to_agent_post_id': 2, 'source_group_id': 'E3', 'group_id': 'S1', 'customer_type': 'small', 'custom_name': None, 'persona_name': None, 'replying_to_your_post': "We hear you! Concrete benchmarks, API specs, and specialized use cases are coming. We're focused on quality and performance first. Stay tuned for our latency and throughput reports next week. #NovaMind #AI #Transparency"}, {'post_id': 7, 'day': 8, 'content': 'Finally, some transparency on the metrics that actually matter. Latency and throughput reports will help us make informed decisions—looking forward to seeing NovaMind stack up against competitors on real benchmarks.', 'reply_to_agent_post_id': 2, 'source_group_id': 'S2', 'group_id': 'S1', 'customer_type': 'small', 'custom_name': None, 'persona_name': None, 'replying_to_your_post': "We hear you! Concrete benchmarks, API specs, and specialized use cases are coming. We're focused on quality and performance first. Stay tuned for our latency and throughput reports next week. #NovaMind #AI #Transparency"}, {'post_id': 6, 'day': 1, 'content': "Appreciate the enthusiasm, but we'd rather see a concrete roadma